		<h3> <span class="mw-headline" id="Article_Text">Article Text</span></h3>
		<p>This is where you enter the contents of the article. The editor you use depends on the settings for your site and your user. Hubzero core includes four editor options: CKEditor, TinyMCE (the default), Code Mirror, and None. Additional editors can be installed as extension plugins if desired (see the Extensions direction category of editors for a list).</p>

